### `extensions/pulseboard/runtime-api.ts`

**Purpose:** Private runtime barrel. Aggregates SDK re-exports needed by `src/` files. Avoids direct deep-imports into the SDK from each `src/` file; keeps all SDK subpath references in one place.

```typescript
// Private runtime barrel for the bundled PulseBoard extension.
// Keep this barrel thin and aligned with the local extension surface.

