Now I see: `outbound?: ChannelOutboundAdapter | ChatChannelAttachedOutboundOptions;`

`ChatChannelAttachedOutboundOptions` is:
```typescript
type ChatChannelAttachedOutboundOptions = {
  base: Omit<ChannelOutboundAdapter, "sendText" | "sendMedia" | "sendPoll">;
  attachedResults: {
    channel: string;
    sendText?: ...
    sendMedia?: ...
    sendPoll?: ...
